Sarkozy Says He Sees ‘Progress’ in Fighting Debt Crisis

-- B y   H e l e n e   F o u q u e t
-- 
2011-10-22T19:33:08Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-22/sarkozy-says-he-sees-progress-in-fighting-debt-crisis.html
French President  Nicolas Sarkozy 
said he sees “progress” in fighting the euro-area debt crisis
and said a stategy must be in place by an Oct. 26 summit.
Sarkozy is “confident” a structural and ambitious solution
will be found, he told reporters tonight as he arrived at a
meeting before a leaders’ meeting in Brussels tomorrow.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Helene Fouquet in Paris at 
